WEBVTT

00:03.433 --> 00:06.458
We're getting reports of a crime wave across the region.

00:06.542 --> 00:08.667
I'm live outside the West Wallaby Street house

00:08.750 --> 00:12.300
of the evil inventor, Mr. Wallace.

00:12.383 --> 00:13.883
Evil?

00:16.042 --> 00:17.167
I'm innocent.

00:26.183 --> 00:29.625
Who could possibly be behind all this?
